DOTA POS 1 IMPROVEMENT COACH
============================

Project Objective:
Build a Python-based Dota 2 match analyzer
focused on Position 1 players.

--------------------------------

DAY 1 - Project Setup

Completed:
- Created Python project structure
- Setup virtual environment
- Installed requests library
- Connected OpenDota API

Achievement:
Successfully retrieved match data using Match ID.

--------------------------------

DAY 2 - Data Extraction

Completed:
- Retrieved match JSON data
- Explored OpenDota response structure
- Extracted players information
- Retrieved hero database from OpenDota API

Achievement:
Successfully converted hero_id into hero name.

--------------------------------

DAY 3 - Player Identification

Completed:
- Created hero mapping system
- Created function to search player based on selected hero
- Successfully detected Spectre player from match

Achievement:
System can identify selected hero performance.

--------------------------------

DAY 4 - Performance Display

Completed:
- Created player performance report

Displayed:
- KDA
- Last Hits
- Denies
- GPM
- XPM
- Net Worth
- Hero Damage
- Tower Damage